  <h1>Support</h1>

  <h2>Get in touch</h2>
  <p>Email us at <a href="mailto:support@sunpebblelabs.com">support@sunpebblelabs.com</a> —
     we usually reply within two days.</p>

  <h2>Restore your purchase</h2>
  <p>Reinstalled or got a new phone? Open Sleeptab → Settings → <em>Restore Purchase</em>.
     The unlock is tied to your Apple ID, so you'll never pay twice.</p>

  <h2>No sleep data showing?</h2>
  <p>Sleeptab needs permission to read sleep from Apple Health. Check Settings → Health →
     Data Access &amp; Devices → Sleeptab, and make sure your watch or sleep tracker is
     writing sleep to Health.</p>

  <h2>Where is my data?</h2>
  <p>On your device, always. See the <a href="/sleeptab/privacy/">Privacy Policy</a>.</p>
</Base>
